"Your traveling to another dimension, A dimension not only of sight and sound but of mind. A wonderous land who's boundries are that of imagination. There's the sign post up ahead! Your next stop, The Twilight Zone..." 



In this map you travel through 3 classic 'Twilight Zone' episodes. TZ fans will probably enjoy this and others... well I dont know how this map is on the gameplay end. Please give it a go and let me know what ya think. Oh and if you start at CT dont run forward in the wormhole it'll hurt ya...
